    "text": [
        "Dear Sir/Madam,",
        "My name is Akshay Shrivastava. I am writing this letter to inform you about my missing card which I was supposed to get from your bank. Moreover, the envelope which I got from the courier company",
        "does not contain any card and it was empty.",
        "This is a very serious concern and I request you to please look into it as soon as possible. This particular card is linked to my salary account. I am assuming that someone has gone through my mailbox and possibly stolen it.",
        "I would request you to block the card. And please let me know what formalities I have to follow to get the new card. It would be a great help if the bank can send an executive to my place for further assistance. And do I also have to submit a police FIR of my lost card ?",
        "Looking forward to hearing from your end at the earliest",
        "Regards",
        "Akshay Shrivastava"
